title: How Christianity Changed the World -  Alvin J. Schmidt
description:
How Christianity Changed the World -  Alvin J. Schmidt   epub/mobi

A survey of the various ways--often unrecognized and overlooked--whereby Christianity has impacted the world. Western civilisation and its values and freedoms did not rise in a vacuum but developed because of the beliefs and ideas of those who lived their lives in the Judaeo-Christian value system. Other societies with different belief systems developed in a very different ways...
